reviews.ReviewText: I was so excited when I ran across this cereal in the store. I love blueberry and lemon together. However, I was soooo disappointed. These lemon clusters are so fake tasting they make me nauseous. I now pick them out of the cereal while I’m eating it, but I can’t stand to look at them. They look like giant tonsil stones!

reviews.Title: Skip this one
reviews.ReviewText: I love the fruit and yogurt cereal but this one is not good. There isn’t enough of a blueberry flavor and there also isn’t a huge lemon flavor unless you bite into one of the bits.

reviews.Title: Great taste combination. A bit sweet.
reviews.ReviewText: Special-K with fresh blueberries has always been a favorite combination for me. The lemon zest adds a bit of zing. A bit sweeter than I would have made it. But overall it's a great taste combination.

reviews.Title: Too lemon
reviews.ReviewText: Overall not bad, but tasting lemon strong. Recommend to citrus fans.

reviews.Title: Favorite of all the flavors!
reviews.ReviewText: I this flavor more than any of the other flavors. Also like pumpkin in the fall.

reviews.Title: blueberries are perfectly capable of standing alon
reviews.ReviewText: I tried this because I like blueberries. It is a horrible taste combination. Who said while developing this cereal:: Wow, blueberries would be awesome if only they were covered with lemon oat clusters. Please fire that person. A needless solution in search of a problem that does not exist . Please fix.

reviews.Title: My favorite cereal!!!!!!
reviews.ReviewText: This is my favorite cereal! The milk only enhances the blueberry and lemon flavors. They have gotten the strength of the flavor just right where it is not overwhelming but strong enough it leaves a pleasant taste on the pallet. I just wish is came in a bigger box.
Delicious cereal at a great price!
I love this cereal. I wish the box was a little bigger since my husband keeps stealing my cereal.

reviews.Title: Tasty Breakfast and Snack
reviews.ReviewText: This has been one of my favorites since it first arrived in stores!

reviews.Title: Great Taste.
reviews.ReviewText: Nice crunch and multiple flavors. Doesn't get soggy quickly.

reviews.Title: Like the taste
reviews.ReviewText: I got it a t NEX but have not seen it at other stores yet

reviews.Title: Delicious!
reviews.ReviewText: Tasted wonderful! Loved the combo of lemon & blueberry—very unique.

reviews.Title: Lose the lemon clusters
reviews.ReviewText: This is good without the lemon clusters. They have a an aftertaste like that of machine oil. I I had to pick them out the bowl, halfway through the box I gave up and gave the rest to the squirrels. Might be better to add the blueberries to Raisin Bran.

reviews.Title: Kellogg's Blueberry, Lemony Clusters
reviews.ReviewText: I tried Kellogg's Special K's Blueberry Lemon cereal and was amazedathow refreshingly flavorful it is. Crunchy and tangy with a lingering lemony twist to it's nourishing and satisfying taste, Kellogg's Blueberry With Lemon Clusters have won me over. Now, it's become my favorite.

reviews.Title: A Mild Blueberry Taste
reviews.ReviewText: I enjoyed this cereal. I am not a big blueberry fan but my husband likes blueberry. I was pleasantly surprised since the blueberry and lemon didn't have an overwhelming taste. I liked this cereal and will buy it again.

reviews.Title: Not a good mix
reviews.ReviewText: My hubby and I were not impressed with the combination of flavors. Every other mix we have eaten has been great.

reviews.Title: The Best! Ever!
reviews.ReviewText: Easily the best cereal I've ever had! And over the past 81 years, I've had a few.

This is one of the best cereals EVER as are the Special K cereals vanilla almond, and the fruit & yogurt. I only wish they all had less sugar. The blueberry taste isn’t overwhelming and the lemon clusters are a sweet lemon and not a tart flavor. I have been known to eat cereal for dinner-a lot, and as a snack, and as a lunch. Can’t beat a bowl of cereal with super cold milk.

reviews.Title: Special K Blueberry Lemon
reviews.ReviewText: I love this cereal and I have a very hard time finding it in my area. It is just the right sweet with a little tart. And the flakes stay crunchy.

reviews.Title: Blueberry galore!
reviews.ReviewText: We so look forward to this product again. What a full flavor of blueberries!

reviews.Title: Love my special k
reviews.ReviewText: Tasting for breakfast or a snack crip taste of the lemon cluster and blueberry nuggets.

reviews.Title: New Special K cereal flavor
reviews.ReviewText: I thought the Special K cereal Blueberry Lemon sounded interesting so I tried it. It’s delicious. Loved the Special K flakes and the Blueberry Lemon pieces were crunchy and tasty. Will definitely buy again.

reviews.Title: Absolutely best cereal ever
reviews.ReviewText: This cereal is honestly the very best I have ever eaten. The sweet blueberry contrasted with the perfect lemony goodness is just awesome. I have a terribly hard time finding this cereal though

reviews.Title: Very Yummy!
reviews.ReviewText: I recently purchase Kellogg's Special K Blueberry Lemon Cereal, which I had not previously tried. It was absolutely delicious. It was crunch and not to sweet. The tart lemon was a lovely complement to the sweet blueberries. I will definitely purchase this again.

reviews.Title: Taste Great
reviews.ReviewText: The only breakfast cereal I eat is Special K. The Blueberry Lemon is absolutely delicious! It is not always available at the store where I shop so when I see it I buy it!

reviews.Title: Thought id love it
reviews.ReviewText: I was excited by this combo and eager to get it. But i was very disappointed. The mix isn't right. Neither flavor comes through enough and it just tastes grainy.

reviews.Title: Excellent
reviews.ReviewText: Love the combination of tastes, crunchy with balls of lemon goodness

reviews.Title: Blueberry and lemon
reviews.ReviewText: Blueberry with lemon clusters is my favorite cereal EVER! It's so hard to find in my town, I find a small box like once a month! And I eat it in 20-30 minutes so YUMMY!!!

reviews.Title: Wakeup great taste
reviews.ReviewText: Love this new new tasty lemon and blueberry flavor to compliment the always delicious crunchy flakes. So good for the first meal of the day.

reviews.Title: astranomical
reviews.ReviewText: i don’t leave reviews but im eating this stuff at 3:16 am and it’s astronomical

reviews.Title: special k blueberry
reviews.ReviewText: I am on my 3rd box of this cereal. I t is great tasting.

reviews.Title: Yummy!
reviews.ReviewText: I tried this when it first came out and I really liked it, I had some just this morning

reviews.Title: Blue liscious!
reviews.ReviewText: Very good combination although I was skeptical! Would definitely purchase again :)

reviews.Title: Special k blueberry lemon cereal
reviews.ReviewText: Great taste and fulfilling.Great for breakfast or anytime

reviews.Title: One of the Better Sp. Ks
reviews.ReviewText: Healthy and tastes very good. My only complaint is clusters wording. I think it is called Blueberry with Lemon Clusters but I think there are also blueberry clusters and maybe oat clusters.

reviews.Title: great
reviews.ReviewText: loved it, especially the lemon clusters. great flavor

reviews.Title: The best non original Special K cereal
reviews.ReviewText: I was very disappointed when you discontinued Blueberry Special K, but so happy you brought back Special K Cereal Blueberry lemon. This has been my wife's and my favorite cereal.

reviews.Title: Blueberry cereal
reviews.ReviewText: we buy 3 boxes at a time of the blueberry lemon cereal. ABSOLUTELY the best!!!!!

reviews.Title: Really great taste.
reviews.ReviewText: The blueberry flakes are delicious by themselves, but when you get a bite of flakes with the little clusters....YUM! Our Family loves Special K Blueberry Lemon.

reviews.Title: Special K Blueberry Lemon
reviews.ReviewText: Kellogg's Special K Blueberry Lemon is a good tasting cereal. This was my first time trying this variety, and it satisfied my tastebuds.

reviews.Title: Run don’t walk
reviews.ReviewText: I stopped eating cereal a couple years ago. Saw this and decided to try it. I am now eating it daily, it is so delicious. The lemon flavor is in every bite. I do add blueberries to it because there are not a lot of them in it. Great job Kellogg!

reviews.Title: My favorite cereal!!!
reviews.ReviewText: I did not think I would like this. I tried it because of a recommendation. Now it is my favorite of all time.

reviews.Title: blueberry-lemon lover delight
reviews.ReviewText: Blueberry & lemon are my absolute FAVORITE flavor combination and Kellogg's certainly got the balance right. Too often either the lemon can be overpowering and you lose the subtle flavor of the blueberries, but this cereal nailed it!

reviews.Title: Great Taste with a Crunch
reviews.ReviewText: I curiously bought this over a year ago and am glad I did. Great combinations of ingredients providing a mouthful of flavor with a crunch. Eat by itself or add strawberries and bananas .

reviews.Title: Great.
reviews.ReviewText: Usually always buy the strawberry decided to r=try different flavor blueberry lemon Glad I did.

reviews.Title: Good flavor combination
reviews.ReviewText: I really enjoyed this flavor combination of blueberry and lemon with Special K flakes. Both flavors come out nicely in the combination and makes for a delicious breakfast!

reviews.Title: Mmmm...Blueberries and Lemon!
reviews.ReviewText: I bought this a while ago and Kellogg's asked me for a review so here it goes. I love blueberries with lemon so why wouldn't I like blueberries and lemon in my cereal? The flavors were true to taste and it was a good cereal to have in the winter when fresh fruit is not available

reviews.Title: Great flavor combo
reviews.ReviewText: This is one of my favorite Special K flavors. Unfortunately, the grocery store where I do most of my shopping no longer carries it.

reviews.Title: The combo taste of lemon and blueberry = AMAZING
reviews.ReviewText: I can't get enough of this cereal. I get between 3 and 5 boxes when I go shopping for Special K

reviews.Title: Yum
reviews.ReviewText: I’ve purchased the Kellogg’s Blueberry Lemon cereal several times. It is one of my favorites. The flakes are big and a little sweet without being too sweet with a hint of blueberry flavor. There are also these little treats of crunchy oat blueberry clusters and the lemon nuggets that taste like a lemon drizzle from a pastry. Delish!! Give it try!

reviews.Title: Great taste
reviews.ReviewText: It’s hard to find this flavor but every time I see it on display I must get at least two per shopping trip

reviews.Title: Delicious!
reviews.ReviewText: I really enjoy the Blueberry Lemon Special K cereal. It is one of my favorite flavors.

reviews.Title: Great Taste!
reviews.ReviewText: I've been eating this cereal for some time now, and really enjoy it.

reviews.Title: GREAT !! I LOVE blueberries, etc.
reviews.ReviewText: I LOVE Blueberries and the hint of lemon is delightful, however I find the flakes too large and coarse for my taste !! I chipped a tooth on one of them, Shockingly enough !! I also LOVE the chocolate Special K - (my Favorite) and find those flakes too large and coarse !! This is all I eat for Breakfast and I wish the flakes were smaller, as I have to squash the inner bags to make the cereal nicer to eat - (in my Opinion) !!

reviews.Title: Delicious
reviews.ReviewText: Hope I can find it in the store because I would definitely buy it again!

reviews.Title: Blueberry Lemon
reviews.ReviewText: I really like this cereal, especially the blueberries and the small pieces of lemon.

reviews.Title: Tastes great
reviews.ReviewText: I can not keep a full box in the house, so I learned to buy two boxes at a time.

reviews.Title: Great taste
reviews.ReviewText: This cereal was so good right out of the box or with milk. Delicious!

reviews.Title: Delicious!!
reviews.ReviewText: Definitely one of my favorite Special K flavors!! Don’t get tired of it easily; really yummy!

reviews.Title: Loved it, but unfortunately won't buy it again
reviews.ReviewText: I just tried Honey Bunches of Oats Granola for the first time mixing it with my cereal, and loved the taste. However I was very disappointed when I looked for the recycling logo on the packaging and didn't find it. With recycling being such a common place and expected thing these days, I will choose and use another similar product instead.

reviews.Title: Yummy crunchy healthy!!
reviews.ReviewText: My little daughter loves this. Crunchiness is good. Perfect with milk and some fresh fruit, She loves it as a good snack without milk too. Crunchy, healthy yummy breakfast and for snack. We carry it around when traveling too :)

reviews.Title: DELICIOUS!!
reviews.ReviewText: This is some of the best granola I have ever eaten! My grandmother, would always sneak into it, while watching my little girls. She absolutely loved it! Will definitely buy this again, and again!

reviews.Title: Tasted great
reviews.ReviewText: Love the sweet honey taste of this granola so delicious. I put it on pretty much any kind of yogurt I eat add nice flavor and crunch

reviews.Title: Crunchy goodness
reviews.ReviewText: Honey bunches of oats honey roasted granola is the perfect healthy snack. It can be eaten alone or even mixed in with something like fruit or yogurt.

reviews.Title: Wholesome granola
reviews.ReviewText: Honey Bunches if Oats Honey Roasted Granola was the perfect mix of granola and sweet treat! I often find some granolas way too sweet but not this one. The perfect mix! I enjoyed the clusters. This had a great crunch to it. I found myself munching on it alone, sprinkling it on ice cream and mixing it with yogurt. We will be purchasing this product as a staple in our pantry.

reviews.Title: Delicious
reviews.ReviewText: My family loved this granola. They used it as cereal, toppings on frozen yogurt and regular yogurt, and even on oatmeal

reviews.Title: Tastes Great!
reviews.ReviewText: This Honey Bunches of Oats Granola tastes great! I love the combination of honey and oats! It goes great on yogurt and I can see this being perfect for a topper on salads. The only thing I wish was different is that the bunches of it were smaller. But you can just use your fingers or break them up inside the bag to make them smaller.

reviews.Title: Delicious
reviews.ReviewText: This granola was delicious by itself or mixed in something. I added it to cereal and yogurt but also ate it by itself. It was a great treat that I could have that was healthy and satisfied my desire for something sweet.

reviews.Title: Great Honey Granola Snack!!
reviews.ReviewText: I really like this honey granola snack because it tastes like pure honey and it fills me up and gives me the energy I need to get through my day.

reviews.Title: We love this granola!
reviews.ReviewText: My husband and son both love this granola. Their favorite way to eat it is on top of

reviews.Title: Honey bunches of oats sample
reviews.ReviewText: This granola was amazing! I topped my yogurt with it for breakfast and it was a hit with my family! Definitely recommend!

reviews.Title: Will buy over and over again
reviews.ReviewText: Honey Bunches of Oats Honey Roasted Granola was AMAZING! My kids and I ate it with yogurt and fruit and also stand alone as a cereal. It was soooo yummy! The kids liked it so much that it was gone in a day.

reviews.Title: Delicious and Healthy Snack
reviews.ReviewText: The Honey Bunches of Oats Granola is such a great, quick and easy snack. It's a delicious and healthy healthy alternative to the regular snacks out there. With the granola being honey roasted it make them that much better. The hint of honey was tasty, but not overpowering. It tastes much better than other honey flavored foods and it's one I even shared with my fiancé and our children. It was the perfect snack for me to bring to work, I felt less guilty bringing this than other unhealthy snacks. I already can't wait to buy another bag; quite literally since ours is almost gone!

reviews.Title: Delicious
reviews.ReviewText: This Honey Bunches of Oats Granola is absolutely delicious. Not only is it perfect all by itself but it is so great added to yogurt! It is better than the previous granola I was eating and I just can't get enough of it!

reviews.Title: Delicious by itself
reviews.ReviewText: Honey roasted granola tasted so good I ate it alone most of the time. It gives yogurt the right punch and makes you want to keep eating it. The bag size is awesome. Especially for a big family like mine. There are no big chunks of granola so serving it and eating it is a breeze. I would definitely recommend this brand and flavor.

reviews.Title: Surprisingly Good
reviews.ReviewText: Loved this, and oddly enough, so did the kids! Will definitely be purchasing more along with any other variations that may be available!! I received this sample free from Influenster for testing purposes, all opinions are 100% honest and up to date.

reviews.Title: Amazing
reviews.ReviewText: I really loved eating this wholesome Honey Bunches of Oats Granola in the morning with my tea. My children also loved to eat it as a snack. We all enjoyed it so much that we went out and definitely brought more.

reviews.Title: Great Crunchy addition
reviews.ReviewText: I have always loved Honey Bunches of Oats and so have my kids. We put the granola on our yogurt, eat it like cereal, and sometimes eat it by itself. It's so yummy just like the cereal only crunchier.

reviews.Title: Delicious!
reviews.ReviewText: Honey Bunches of Oats Honey Roasted Granola is amazing. We've used it in out oatmeal, yogurt, and as a snack during a trip to the zoo. It's a delicious treat, and really kicks yogurt and oatmeal up a notch!

reviews.Title: Pretty good for granola!
reviews.ReviewText: I'm not the biggest fan of granola usually because it's usually too bland for me but this granola has the perfect punch of flavor. It's not too hard like some where you're afraid you'll chip a tooth or pull out that filling, it has the perfect crunch too it. I like that this granola has enough flavor that you can eat it with plain, add some fresh fruit, or even in your yogurt. The flavor makes it very versatile.

reviews.Title: Super yummy snack
reviews.ReviewText: Really great snack for on the go with the kids. Its just sweet enough and a great crunch. I also really liked the way it is packaged. Its a great size and easy to open.

reviews.Title: Honey Bunches of Oats Honey Roasted Granola
reviews.ReviewText: This granola is quite satisfying. It is crunchy, has great flavor, and doesn't get soggy. The honey flavor is better than most that I have tried. I would definitely buy this product again and recommended it to my family and friends. Perfect snack for the work day.

reviews.Title: granola
reviews.ReviewText: taste exactly like the cereal! great for parfait or even by itself. doesn't get soggy to fast.

reviews.Title: So Delicious!
reviews.ReviewText: My kids and I love this granola! It has a great texture and flavor. We used it on cereal and smoothies and even ice cream. I definitely will be buy this regularly!

reviews.Title: Perfect snack
reviews.ReviewText: I love how the extra crunchiness of Honey Bunches of Oats Honey Granola. It's great on yogurt or added to a bowl of cereal. The kids love it too and it's a healthy alternative for when they want sweets. Very satisfying and flavorful.

reviews.Title: Very tasty
reviews.ReviewText: Its super crunchy and very tasty. I've put it on yogurt and eat it straight from the bag. My kids love it too!

reviews.Title: Honey bunches of oats honey roasted granola
reviews.ReviewText: Oh my gosh these are so delicious. Great for a little go to snack or to add on your yogurt or oatmeal for some crunch. I definitely recommend these to everyone to have in their pantry.

reviews.Title: Perfect lunchbox staple!
reviews.ReviewText: I wasn't sure that my kids would like this granola, but they absolutely love it! It is the perfect lunchbox staple and belly filler. This tastes just like the bunches from Honey Bunches of Oats cereal. It's delicious on it's own or mixed in a snack mix. It's a permanent on my grocery list now.

reviews.Title: Honey Bunches Of Oats
reviews.ReviewText: Great tasting cereal and enjoyable to eat!

reviews.Title: Absolutely fabulous
reviews.ReviewText: I absolutely love Honey Bunches of Oats Granola. It's got an awesome flavor. Is filling and delicious. Can't wait to get more.

reviews.Title: So delicious!
reviews.ReviewText: I'm in love with this cereal! Are so good (i love the granola) I eat the hole bag in 2 days! I need to buy more tomorrow 😁 Everyones need to try this it's so good

reviews.Title: Good taste, a little too sweet
reviews.ReviewText: We received the granola and the packaging is nice and you can see the granola which has big pieces. My kids really liked the granola and ate almost all of it. It wasn't my favorite however because o thought it was too sweet.

reviews.Title: Delicious
reviews.ReviewText: This Honey Bunches of Oats granola is amazing! I've eaten it plain, on yogurt, and like cereal in a bowl with milk. It's delicious all ways. It's tasty and crunchy and adds great flavor and texture to things like my yogurt. Definitely going to add this to my regular cereal rotation.

reviews.Title: " Yummy in My Tummy "
reviews.ReviewText: I carry a bag of these Honey Bunches of Oats Honey Roasted Granola around with me wherever I go. These are such a nutritional, and tasty treat. My whole family loves them. Best of all they are wholesome and made with real honey..

reviews.Title: Snack i feel good about
reviews.ReviewText: Amazing flavor and texture.Kids and Adults can enjoy and feel good about.

reviews.Title: Yummy
reviews.ReviewText: This is perfect for a snack or with yogurt. My kids love it as a snack on the go. Will recommend to family and friends

reviews.Title: Everything you love but better
reviews.ReviewText: I love Honey Bunches of Oats cereal and often add it to my yogurt. This granola version was perfect for that. I hate when things get soggy, this stayed super crunchy until the last bite. The granola version is the best part of the regular cereal so yummy and crunchy.

reviews.Title: Perfect work snack!
reviews.ReviewText: These clusters of honey flavored goodness are the perfect snack while working from home and tending to virtual learning students! Life is stressful right now and kicking back for a few minutes and enjoying Honey Bunches of Oats Honey Roasted Granola is a wonderful pick-me-up!

reviews.Title: Delicious, filling, no weird after taste
reviews.ReviewText: This is a delicious, lightly sweetened granola. I've eaten similar products that leave a weird aftertaste. This just tastes like granola! I typically eat it with yogurt. It is a wonderful start to my morning.

reviews.Title: Taste Amazing!!
reviews.ReviewText: Great product taste amazing especially if you put some in your yogurt or oatmeal makes a fast easy breakfast even better.

reviews.Title: Very good snack
reviews.ReviewText: This granola mix has a very good flavor and great as a snack. They are not sticky like some others. I would recommend this product and plan on buying more.

reviews.Title: Even the kids loved it!
reviews.ReviewText: Our family are huge fans of Honey Bunches of Oats. The one child that is not much so, liked the granola the most! We did cut the serving size in half to help cut the calorie count in half, but we truly enjoyed the taste! Would definitely buy at the store!

reviews.Title: Super Crunch
reviews.ReviewText: I love the very crunchy texture this granola has. The taste is exception and I love putting it in my morning fruit and yogurt.

reviews.Title: So good
reviews.ReviewText: Please put this yummy goodness in MORE STORES!!! This can be eaten straight from the bag (like my 15 yr old likes to do), or you can add it to a boring cereal, or perhaps one that gyps (sounds like "jips") you with the amount, or lack thereof, clusters, haha......or add it to yogurt, etc. ~So many uses, just wish it was more widely available! My son

reviews.Title: Wholesome and nutritious.
reviews.ReviewText: I Loved the fact that this was in the flavor of Honey roasted. I defiantly tasted similar to the cereal from this brand. I placed some on yogurt, and on top of ice-cream and it was delish. The product its self came in a sturdy bag that was easy to close and open.

reviews.Title: Mom Loved it Family Didn't
reviews.ReviewText: As a Honey Bunches of Oat Fan I thought that this product was DELICIOUS! I was able to eat it straight out of the bag and it gave you the same flavor as the cereal. it was really addicting However my husband and son didn't like it at all they said that is was too hard and dry and not something they would reach for if this was in the house.

reviews.Title: Yummy!
reviews.ReviewText: I've never tried granola like this before. But it was really good! The honey made it sweet so like a crumbled up granola bar. Perfect for topping yogurts or oatmeal or adding to cereal. I sat and ate provable a quarter of the bag just like a snack. Also approved by my very picky three year old. She thinks they are delicious bee treats

reviews.Title: Great taste
reviews.ReviewText: Honey Bunches of Oats Honey Roasted Granola tastes great. I love the honey on them. I eat it as a snack, but would also be great as topping on yogurt. I would definitely recommend trying it.

reviews.Title: Yummy way to wake up!
reviews.ReviewText: This is my new favorite granola! I cannot wait to get up and have some during my morning routine. It is a perfect crunchy bite everytime. It is also very filling. Love this granola!

reviews.Title: My new fav
reviews.ReviewText: One of the best I've tried. It's pretty good and just the right amount of honey in each bite I would definitely buy again!

reviews.Title: Cereal is Better
reviews.ReviewText: Honey Bunches of Oats granola is okay. I tried eating it on its own as a snack but the cluster sizes vary quite a bit and there were a lot of small pieces which made picking them up difficult. I also tried using it as a topping on greek yogurt. That again was ok but the consistency was not as good as my usual granola. It was chewier than I like and not as crisp. Again cluster sizes varied a lot where some pieces were too big to go with a spoonful of yogurt while others were too small to be noticeable. I was surprised that Honey Bunches of Oats granola had more calories and sugar per serving then my usual granola but didn't taste as sweet. As it stands, the granola is ok but I would rather just eat the cereal and stick with my current brand of granola.

reviews.Title: Yummy
reviews.ReviewText: I enjoyed the taste. Not too sweet. I like the texture and how it absorbs the milk. Very grainy like.

reviews.Title: Just the right amount of sweetness!
reviews.ReviewText: My family was already a fan of Honey Bunches of Oats cereal, so I was excited to receive this new snack for review. I'm not really a granola person... or at least I didn't think I was. This is almost better than the cereal! You get all the yummy "bunches" and don't have to worry about the flakes getting soggy, if you decide to eat it with milk. It's like having a marshmallow cereal without the cereal, only you won't have to worry about crater-like cavities as a result. I have finally found a late-night snack that I won't feel so guilty about.

reviews.Title: Kid approved
reviews.ReviewText: Opening this i knew i was gonna love this!! But my kids got one taste and stole the whole bag!! Im glad they like a healthy alternative to chips and junk food. Ill be buying more of these and in all the flavors

reviews.Title: Great granola, great price point!
reviews.ReviewText: We actually had just bought a bag of another flavor of this granola because my daughter wanted to try it on her yogurt. Then surprise I get a bag of the honey roasted to sample! It's delicious right out of the bag but also makes a great addition to yogurt, Frosted Flakes, and evening on top of oatmeal! We will definitely be buying this again!

reviews.Title: Delicious Snack
reviews.ReviewText: I was excited to try this sample. We don't usually buy granola but we enjoy eating it. I loved the sizes of granola clusters, not huge but big enough to eat a handful and give to my toddlers as a snack. They are not overly sweet but still have a great honey taste. It's delicious on yogurt or eaten dry as well.

reviews.Title: Pretty Good for Granola
reviews.ReviewText: The granola has a pretty good flavor. It would be better in yogurt or something similar. The granola is overly dry but has a great flavor.

reviews.Title: Absolutely Delicious
reviews.ReviewText: My family fell in love with this product! It is crunchy, sweet, and super fresh!

reviews.Title: Crisp fresh taste
reviews.ReviewText: Healthy, good taste and fantastic with a banana sliced into it.

reviews.Title: Best Cereal
reviews.ReviewText: This is the only cereal box I purchase. Quality, good ingredients, and overall appropriate in it's sweetness ! Never lets me down.

reviews.Title: Amazing!!!
reviews.ReviewText: great cereal. Would recommend! Skeptical at first but really a great buy for only $2.99. WHAT A STEAL!!!!!

reviews.Title: Yummy
reviews.ReviewText: My favorite cereal :) and it's cheaper at target than most places!

reviews.Title: Honey Oats
reviews.ReviewText: It taste very delicious. Never go wrong with honey oats!!

reviews.Title: Perfect combination and a staple in our house.
reviews.ReviewText: This is my husband’s favorite cereal. He asks me to buy 2-3 boxes at a time. I don’t eat cereal but he said this is the perfect combination of Frosted Flakes and granola! The price is steep compared to other cereals and the box is way smaller.

reviews.Title: I Love this stuff!
reviews.ReviewText: I'll never need another kind of cereal, Ever!

reviews.Title: Yuck
reviews.ReviewText: I love regular HBO, but not a fan of the frosted ones. Bought them to try because it was the only thing left on the rack after a post cereal sale. (I guess I'm not alone in thinking they're yuck). The frosted ones are crunchier-- in a not enjoyable way-- and they have less flavor. Seems that some people here like them a lot, but I don't why. They taste stale and seem like an unhealthy evil twin version of something that's actually good. I didn't enjoy them & I won't be buying them again.

reviews.Title: Fuel to start your day
reviews.ReviewText: I like the taste not over powering with sugar.

reviews.Title: Love Love Love!
reviews.ReviewText: I love the taste and it is fortified with iron, thank you so much! I have a hard time getting it in foods I like.

reviews.Title: of all the honey bunches of oats I like this one the best

reviews.ReviewText: I love this cereal and it is by far my favorite one to eat!! I love the flavor of the honey, granola and almonds all mixed together. There are a few different varieties of Honey Bunches of Oats that all taste great and aren't too sweet!! I feel as though it could have a little bit more almonds in it though. I highly recommend this cereal and I will continue to buy it!!

Not the worst out there, but certainly not the best either.

Definitely a good alternative to the sugary cereals my kids usually go for. We will be buying more of this for sure.

I think I prefer the original honey bunches of oats and feel the almonds don't add much. But maybe I'm not a nut person. I'll stick to the original or one of m my other cereal favs in the future.
